title: Nathan Sykes strips it back for new single 'Over And Over Again' - Music
text: Nathan Sykes channels his emotional side for brand new single 'Over And Over Again', which hears him strip it back with just his piano.The former Wanted boyband member will officially release the track on November 20, though it's available to download and stream now.It's the second cut to be lifted from his forthcoming solo debut album, which is expected to follow in 2016.It serves as the follow-up to his first solo single 'Kiss Me Quick', which reached number 14 in the UK and topped the Billboard Dance Chart earlier this year. Nathan has been working with a host of top songwriting talent for his new album, including Babyface, Harmony Samuels and Diane Warren.The 22-year-old scored 10 Top 10 hits during his time in The Wanted, including chart-toppers 'All Time Low' and 'Glad You Came'.
